snippet.title: Amber Heard confirms she'll return for Aquaman 2 [News]
snippet.description:
Amber Heard will return to The Worlds of DC for Aquaman 2.The Justice League star has confirmed to Entertainment Weekly that she will be reprising her role as Xebelean princess Mera for director James Wan's sequel.  ...
